io.mobitech.content_server.model

Class ContentResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.mobitech.content_server.model.ContentResponse

  • public class ContentResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    The content recommendation response will be a JSON formatted string that contains the response sessionId and a recommendation list. In case a callback parameter is specified, the response will be padded with a callback.

      • sessionId

        public java.lang.String sessionId
        Mobitech session id. The value from the last request in a session should be saved and send in any subsequent request or event notification. Note that the this value might changed from request to request, hence important to save the last value from every request.
